# Deploy after every change

After completing any code change in this project:

1. Run `npm run build` and fix failures before deploying.
2. Commit with a clear message describing why the change was made.
3. Push to `origin/main` on `https://github.com/Maditoio/priommo-academy.git`.
4. Tell the user the commit hash and that Vercel is deploying.

Do not wait for the user to ask to deploy. Skip only if there are no file changes to commit, or if the user explicitly says not to deploy.
